snippet.title: Floating Cloud God Saves the Pilgrims in HD! (PS Vita) | E3 2013
snippet.description:
Floating Cloud God Saves the Pilgrims in HD! is a remake of the popular PSP™ game. Recreated with high-definition visuals and PlayStation®Vita exclusive features, this is the definitive version of one of 2012's best-loved PSP™ games.

Vita exclusive features: Trophies, new controls, remastered HD graphics and audio.
